@item User-specified names, which can be either local symbol names or source
program identifiers
@item Reserved OpenSDL keywords
@item Expressions
@end itemize
@cindex Identifiers, user specified

The following can also be used within a @code{MODULE} declaration; although
they are not OpenSDL language elements (@ref{Local Comments} through
@ref{INCLUDE Statement}):
@cindex INCLUDE statement
@cindex Local comments

@itemize @bullet
@item Local and output, line and block, comments
@item @code{INCLUDE} statement
@item Conditional compilation
@item Text pass-through
@item @code{DECLARE} statement
@end itemize
@cindex Comments
@cindex Conditional compilation
@cindex DECLARE statement
@cindex Local comments
