BOOLEAN
@end example

@strong{@code{BOOLEAN}}
@indentedblock
Produces a Boolean variable in the output file.
@end indentedblock

The following is an example of the @code{BOOLEAN} keyword used in an
@code{ITEM} declaration:

@example
ITEM true BOOLEAN;
@end example
