@indentedblock
The @code{ALIGN} and NOALIGN keywords can be used to align (or de-align) the
members of an aggregate on their natural boundary.  The @code{BASEALIGN}
keyword ensures that the size of an aggregate is a multiple of the given
alignment.  The @code{BASEALIGN} keyword therefore takes an argument, which
